name: No.B14
description:
Part historical research into whimsy, part modern twist on spiritual adornment.

-Fabrication-
Mix of hand-cut peach, white & grey Moonstones from India (aprox. 2.5 & 3.5mm)
Hand Knotted 1.5mm French metallic cord
Designed for all-day & everyday wear.

-Details & Fit-
6-7.5” Fit (adjustable)
Finishes at the back with knotted delicate tassels and a Moonstone at pull-tie closure

Moonstone is a stone of soothing & calming feminine energy that assists in brightening emotions.  
Additionally it is a reminder of divinity and that all things are a part of a cycle of constant change.
